针对您查询慢的问题，我提供几个优化方案：

1. 缓存层优化

```java
// 使用Caffeine或Redis缓存查询结果
@Component
public class DataQueryService {
    @Autowired
    private CacheManager cacheManager;
    
    // 缓存最近访问的历史数据
    public List<DataRecord> queryWithCache(Date date, String query) {
        String cacheKey = buildCacheKey(date, query);
        
        // 先查缓存
        List<DataRecord> cached = cacheManager.get(cacheKey);
        if (cached != null) return cached;
        
        // 缓存未命中则查询
        List<DataRecord> result = queryFromDuckDB(date, query);
        
        // 异步缓存结果
        CompletableFuture.runAsync(() -> 
            cacheManager.put(cacheKey, result, 30, TimeUnit.MINUTES));
            
        return result;
    }
}
```

