5. S3查询优化配置

```java
@Configuration
public class DuckDBConfig {
    
    @Bean
    public DuckDBConnection duckDBConnection() throws SQLException {
        Connection conn = DriverManager.getConnection("jdbc:duckdb:");
        
        // 优化S3访问配置
        try (Statement stmt = conn.createStatement()) {
            // 启用更快的S3访问
            stmt.execute("SET s3_region='us-east-1'");
            stmt.execute("SET s3_access_key_id='your-key'");
            stmt.execute("SET s3_secret_access_key='your-secret'");
            stmt.execute("SET s3_use_ssl=true");
            
            // 增加并行度
            stmt.execute("SET threads TO 8");
            
            // 优化内存使用
            stmt.execute("SET memory_limit='4GB'");
        }
        
        return new DuckDBConnection(conn);
    }
}
```

6. 文件格式和分区优化

```sql
-- 方案A：使用Parquet格式并添加分区
-- 确保S3数据是按分区存储的
-- s3://bucket/data/year=2024/month=01/day=01/file.parquet

-- 创建外部表，利用分区过滤
CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE historical_data 
USING PARQUET
LOCATION 's3://bucket/data/'
OPTIONS (
    'partitionColumns' 'year,month,day'
);

-- 查询时利用分区剪枝
SELECT * FROM historical_data 
WHERE year = 2024 AND month = 01 AND day = 01;
```

7. 架构改进建议

方案A：混合存储架构

```
本地DuckDB (热数据: 最近5天 + 高频历史)
    ↑
缓存层 (Redis/Memcached)
    ↑
S3 (冷数据归档)
```

方案B：查询代理模式

```java
@RestController
public class QueryController {
    
    @GetMapping("/query")
    public ResponseEntity<QueryResult> query(
            @RequestParam LocalDate startDate,
            @RequestParam LocalDate endDate) {
        
        // 1. 快速响应 - 先返回本地数据
        QueryResult immediateResult = queryLocalData(startDate, endDate);
        
        // 2. 异步查询S3历史数据
        CompletableFuture<QueryResult> historyFuture = 
            queryHistoryAsync(startDate, endDate);
        
        // 3. 可以WebSocket推送或轮询获取完整结果
        return ResponseEntity.accepted()
            .header("X-Query-Id", queryId)
            .body(immediateResult);
    }
}
```

